Subject: [M148] Propagate invitation flag for isolated connections

Original change's description:
> Propagate invitation flag for isolated connections
>
> This is mainly in response to the bug... it does look like not
> propagating the flag in an isolated connection *seems* wrong and there
> doesn't seem to be any comment indicating why this omission is
> necessary.
>
> I didn't bother fixing *all* the plumbings, as it looks like this is
> a deprecated path, anyway.
